headline: Snacking giant Hershey adding more ‘on trend’ ingredients to its sweets lineup
summary: The Reese's and Kit Kat manufacturer is incorporating things such as peanut butter and wafers into its offerings to meet consumer demand, even if that means reducing its dependence on chocolate.
